metadata.name: REBIRTH
metadata.description:
The creator of 33sky made the first NFT collection “3S” - dedicated to full accepting yourself…body, spirit and mind. 

The collection opens with “REBIRTH” - the girl's silver body blazes in a flames of fire. 

The fire represents her energy, which purifies and heals her, it is the path of acceptance and unconditional love.

 “You have a light inside, show it…don’t  hide”.

Model & Art direction: Christina 33sky
Photo: Pavel Dvoyanov 

Instagram: @33sky_____
